{{Unbulleted list|Kunioshitomi no Kami was born to {{ill|Torinaruminokami|ja|鳥鳴海神}} and {{ill|Hinaterinukatabichioikochini no Kami|ja|日名照額田毘道男伊許知邇神}}. Kunioshitomi no Kami married {{ill|Ashinadaka no Kami|ja|葦那陀迦神}} and had a child, {{ill|Hayamikanotakesahayajinumi no Kami|ja|速甕之多気佐波夜遅奴美神}}.}}

- '''Kayanarumi Lineage'''  
{{Unbulleted list|In the genealogical records of Susa Shrine, Kunioshitomi no Kami is listed as a descendant of {{ill|Kayanarumi no Kami|ja|カヤナルミ}}, an offspring of Ōkuninushi. The deity is also noted as the ancestor of the Susa clan, with a child named Kumoyama no Kami, though the consort and mother are not specified.}}

